<item>
            <title>[LU-3597] packet-lustre.c opcodes out of sync with lustre_idl.h</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3597</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On v2_4_52_0-2-g809d46b, the last MDS opcode in lustre_idl.h is MDS_SWAP_LAYOUTS = 61 (added by 4af3ab19), while the last MDS opcode in packet-lustre.c is MDS_GET_INFO = 53. What is the mechanism for keeping these files in sync?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="19845">LU-3597</key>
            <summary>packet-lustre.c opcodes out of sync with lustre_idl.h</summary>
